  {
    "title": "Custom components are awesome",
    "slug": "custom-components",
    "content": {
      "document": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": " Hero Image"
            }
          ],
          "level": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "component-block",
          "component": "hero",
          "props": {
            "imageSrc": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541701494587-cb58502866ab?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80",
            "caption": {
              "discriminant": true,
              "value": null
            }
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "component-block-prop",
              "propPath": ["caption", "value"],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Not all superheroes wear capes. Some write code."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Callout"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "component-block",
          "component": "callout",
          "props": {
            "intent": "info",
            "content": null
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "component-block-prop",
              "propPath": ["content"],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "The really cool stuff is behind the "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "+",
                      "code": true,
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " button on the right of the toolbar – these are the "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Custom Components",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "This component is the "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Callout",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", but you can build your own by defining their data schema (like you do your Keystone schema) and providing a React Component to render the preview."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "They store structured data, and can be inserted (and edited!) anywhere in the document. You can even link them to other items in your database with the "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Relationship",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " field type."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "component-block",
          "component": "callout",
          "props": {
            "intent": "success",
            "content": null
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "component-block-prop",
              "propPath": ["content"],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Custom components",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " can also have props that are edited with an inline form, for more complex use cases (including "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "conditional fields",
                      "italic": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ")."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Once you build your own custom components, your content authors can insert them via the formatting toolbar and your front-end gets structured data to render the components however necessary, eg. "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "you can render your custom components in your frontend using your own design system",
                      "italic": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Quote"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "component-block",
          "component": "quote",
          "props": {
            "content": null,
            "attribution": null
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "component-block-prop",
              "propPath": ["content"],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "A wise person always says wise things"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "component-inline-prop",
              "propPath": ["attribution"],
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "a wise person"
